# verif_matrix.yaml - verification tracking for IP '{{ ip }}' (uvm-gen v{{ tool_version }})
#
# One record is appended per simulation run by sim/scripts/cfg_tool.py
# (invoked from 'make run' / 'make waves'; vManager regressions go through the
# same path). Human-auditable and machine-queryable (a YAML list of records):
#   - config_name : configuration the run used (from its YAML / banner)
#   - param_hash  : FNV-1a signature of the full parameter set
#   - test, seed, result (pass|fail), uvm_errors, uvm_fatals
#   - coverage    : % when available (null otherwise)
#   - date, git_rev, log, params
#
# 'make matrix' prints the per-configuration summary from this file.
# uvm-gen NEVER overwrites this file, not even with --force.
